Class ClassHelper<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.raistlic.common.reflection.ClassHelper<E>

    public final class ClassHelper<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    A helper class that binds to a specified Class instance, and help with getting different types of information from it.
